## 4. Motion Vocabulary

| Motion name       | Duration                | Easing              | Used when                                  |
|-------------------|-------------------------|---------------------|--------------------------------------------|
| Enter — slide up  | `--duration-normal`     | `--easing-enter`    | Cards, list items appearing                |
| Exit — fade out   | `--duration-fast`       | `--easing-exit`     | Toasts dismissing                          |
| Expand — height   | `--duration-normal`     | `--easing-standard` | Accordion, collapsible sections            |
| Transition — page | `--duration-slow`       | `--easing-standard` | Route changes                              |
| Micro — hover     | `--duration-fast`       | `--easing-standard` | Button scale, link underline               |

